{"tid":1555351,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"兒童遊戲：黑警捉乖仔","createTime":"2019-09-09T10:24:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T17:59:00.000Z","uid":316098,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d2badcc95ab60f2e4d8ae12d83443b46a30d1621","tid":1555351,"uid":316098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T10:24:03.000Z","msg":"新城市連日有BB仔同小學生嗌口號。<br />\n今日係公園亦疑似聽到幼稚園生成班fd嗌。<br />\n<br />\n其實呢次運動主要骨幹年齡層，係1x-3x歲咁上下。而當我地變老，<strong>難保有朝一日，唔會好似家下啲藍絲廢老一樣</strong>，失去鬥志，逆來順受。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">所以，我地必須靠自己教育下一代。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n歌曲、遊戲，最能家傳戶曉。<br />\n我動議： <strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">將麻鷹捉雞仔，改成黑警捉乖仔。</span></span></strong>等小朋友一代一代，知道警察唔可以高傲自大， 一定要謙卑服務人民。<strong><ins>(食古不化嘅大陸小朋友就無人陪佢玩嚕。)</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n 希望小小意見能作引玉之資。 大家不妨講下有咩兒童遊戲，可以承傳落去。"},{"pid":"8eca412cbd5f5b65a55220466858128955dcae61","tid":1555351,"uid":298115,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T10:32:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3f1c714e6e5fe6264817b59a39bc722dfe87ba8f","tid":1555351,"uid":316098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8eca412cbd5f5b65a55220466858128955dcae61","tid":1555351,"uid":298115,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T10:32:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T10:37:09.000Z","msg":"😂呢個正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n123紅綠燈 拆鐵馬要小心"},{"pid":"5b14e7769a3848e2020e9cfbefb8aaebc9b89068","tid":1555351,"uid":316098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3f1c714e6e5fe6264817b59a39bc722dfe87ba8f","tid":1555351,"uid":316098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8eca412cbd5f5b65a55220466858128955dcae61","tid":1555351,"uid":298115,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T10:32:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T10:37:09